---
const features = [
  { text: "Devis gratuit" },
  { text: "Intervention rapide" },
  { text: "Garantie décennale" },
  { text: "Produits professionnels" }
];

const cities = [
  "La Seyne-sur-Mer",
  "Six-Fours-les-Plages",
  "Hyères",
  "La Valette-du-Var"
];
---

<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>À Propos</h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="lead">Artisan peintre qualifié basé à Toulon, je mets mon expertise au service de vos projets de rénovation et d'embellissement.</p>
        <p>Spécialisé dans la peinture intérieure et extérieure, je garantis un travail soigné et des finitions impeccables pour transformer vos espaces.</p>
        <div class="features-grid">
          {features.map(feature => (
            <div class="feature-item">
              <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
              <span>{feature.text}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-area">
        <h3>Zone d'Intervention</h3>
        <div class="cities-grid">
          {cities.map(city => (
            <div class="city-item">{city}</div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: rgb(var(--background));
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }
  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    color: rgb(var(--primary));
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    position: relative;
  }
  h2::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 60px;
    height: 4px;
    background: rgb(var(--accent));
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: rgb(var(--primary));
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .feature-icon {
    color: rgb(var(--accent));
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .service-area {
    background: rgb(var(--card-bg));
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  .cities-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .city-item {
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: rgb(var(--background));
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>